<s> Visually I want to separate items in a vertical presentation.  </s>
<s> I can do this by alternating colors or by placing a divider between the items.  </s>
<s> This is done to be nice to the visual shopper or simply for aesthetics.  </s>
<s> There's no need for an auditory response.  </s>
<s> If a divider is meant to divide text on the auditory level as well as visual then I need to use an hr .  </s>
<s> This is where two segments of text are separated to remove the confusion of running together two unrelated paragraphs.  </s>
<s> However, this should be done with CSS so that the text is far enough separated to remove any possible confusion.  </s>
<s> Imagine hearing: "Mary had a little lamb whose fleece was white as snow.  </s>
<s> The little lamb would follow" "rule" ( hr ) "Peter Piper picked a peck of peppers."  </s>
<s> The hr is heard as "rule", so that now makes it heard as "Mary had a little lamb whose fleece was white as snow.  </s>
<s> The little lamb would follow rule Peter Piper picked a peck of peppers.".  </s>
<s> Separation of text in the auditory level is extremely hard and would require more than just a simple hr .  </s>
